# MCD API
Monet+ API for MCD

Typical API response:

+ 200 OK
+ 400 BAD REQ
+ 410 GONE
+ 404 NOT FOUND
+ 500 INTERNAL ERROR

# Group Login

API for gift card registration and client login.

## Client registration and login [/client-api/client-login]

### Gift card registration [POST]
This method should be used once for client registration. 
After successfull registration client receives e-mail with confirmation link. 
When confirmed, user receives e-mail with password. Each subsequent call should contain
e-mail (username) and password HTTP Basic authentication header.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "cln":"1234567890123456", 
            "activationCode":"ABCDEFGH",
            "email":"uzivatel@email.cz"
        }
        
+ Response 200

